
<section class="panel">
  <h1>Debug Config (Lab Only)</h1>
  <p>This page intentionally exposes configuration-style information for training purposes.</p>

  <table>
    <tbody>
      <tr><th>Host</th><td><%= config.host %></td></tr>
      <tr><th>Port</th><td><%= config.port %></td></tr>
      <tr><th>LAB_MODE</th><td><%= config.labMode %></td></tr>
      <tr><th>ALLOW_REMOTE</th><td><%= config.allowRemote %></td></tr>
      <tr><th>Session secret preview</th><td><%= config.sessionSecretPreview %>...</td></tr>
      <tr><th>DB path</th><td><%= config.dbPath %></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Demo Secrets</h2>
  <pre><%= JSON.stringify(config.demoSecrets, null, 2) %></pre>

  <p class="muted">
    In production, this route must not exist. Trainers can use this page to discuss configuration exposure, hardcoded secrets, and attack surface discovery.
  </p>
</section>

